name: Global X Active Hybrid Bond and Preferred Share ETF
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objective, by investing in a portfolio of debt and other debt-like securities, including but not limited to hybrid corporate debt, Alternative Tier 1 Capital, such as limited resource capital notes, and income generating equities, including but not limited to preferred securities fixed-rate perpetual, fixed floating rate, retractable and floating rate, of Canadian and U.S. companies. HYBR may hedge some or all of its non-Canadian dollar currency exposure at the discretion of its sub-advisor. The investment objective of HYBR is to seek to provide unitholders with a high level of income.
